[b]Info:[/b]
Mastermind is the upcoming sixth studio album by American rapper Rick Ross, set to be released on March 4, 2014, by Maybach Music Group, Slip-n-Slide Records and Def Jam Recordings. The album features guest appearances from Jay-Z, Jeezy, The Weeknd, Kanye West, Big Sean, Meek Mill, Lil Wayne, French Montana, Diddy, Scarface, Sizzla, Mavado, and Z-Ro. The album was supported by one official single- "The Devil Is a Lie", along with the promotional singles "Box Chevy", "No Games" and "War Ready".
